oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Bank of McLemoresville
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interior view of the Bank of McLemoresville. Josiah Conrad "Connie" McKinney (1877-1958) is standing behind the teller's counter on the right. Zettie Erin Gardner (1887-1980) is standing behind a counter on the far right. Zettie Gardener worked as a bookkeeper for the bank, and Josiah McKinney was a banker
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
